reference: Nieto et al. 2014 European Bees; Atlas_hymenoptera (http://www.atlashymenoptera.net/page.aspx?id=243)

classification goal: subfamily, tribe, and genera, and bombus species

notes: this clade is a paraphyletic assemblage of 4 familes, three of which occur in europe, Ampulicidae is also excluded because it is an exclusive parasite to cockroaches
